rodin (3.9-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial Ubuntu/Debian packaging of the Rodin platform.
  * Force the Eclipse light theme via rodin.ini to avoid a broken mixed
    light/dark UI on dark desktops.
  * Force a light GTK theme (GTK_THEME=Adwaita:light) in the launcher so the
    native SWT/GTK widgets are light too, not just the Eclipse-drawn ones.

 -- Denis Efremov <efremov@linux.com>  Sun, 14 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000
